	<Title>
		Rheumatoid arthritis: Can it affect the lungs?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Although rheumatoid arthritis primarily affects the joints, it can also affect the lungs.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Can rheumatoid arthritis affect your lungs?
	</Question>
